  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Restaurants &amp; Bars</strong></span></p>
<p><strong>Belevedere Restaurant</strong> is famed for its fresh Mediterranean dishes and uninterrupted sea views from its stunning terrace. Taste local specialities and an attentive service as you enjoy a leisurely lunch or dinner.</p>
<p><strong>Arcade Bar</strong> is an elegant space in which to unwind before dinner. Frescoed ceilings and traditional furnishings are framed by views over the Mediterranean and expert staff mix up innovative cocktails.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Pool</strong></span></p>
<p>Belmond Hotel Caruso has one of the most impressive pools on the Amalfi Coast. Set at the highest point in Ravello, the edge of the heated infinity pool peers over the edge of the cliff for uninterrupted, panoramic sea views. Staff offer a drinks service, too meaning you won’t have to leave your sun lounger if you don’t want to.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Spa</strong></span></p>
<p>The wellness centre offers a large range of specialised beauty and spa treatments (payable locally).</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Complimentary shuttle to Amalfi and Positano</li>
<li>Complimentary daily boat trip</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
