  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Village View Rooms</strong> are on the lower floors of the hotel and have been finished in a classic Italian style, many with lovely terraces. Amenities include air conditioning, TV, minibar, safe and a hairdryer. They can sleep up to two adults.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> enjoy views over the rooftops of Ravello or the lemon-scented gardens. They can sleep up to two adults and are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms</strong> are located on the edge of the property and enjoy stunning sea views from the balcony. They can sleep up to two adults and are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Junior</strong> <strong>Suites</strong> and <strong>Suites</strong> are also available on request, please call for more information or to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
